+
+## Comparison: Vendor Kbase vs Panthor
+
+### Feature Matrix
+
+| Feature | Vendor Kbase | Panthor Status | Location |
+|---------|--------------|----------------|----------|
+| Force coherent mode | DTS `system-coherency=0` | ✅ Forced true | `panthor_device.c:38` |
+| AMBA_ENABLE coherency | R-M-W bits 0-4 = 0 (ACE_LITE) | ✅ **Implemented** | `panthor_gpu.c:61-76` |
+| AMBA shareable cache | Set bit 5 when coherent | ✅ **Implemented** | `panthor_gpu.c:87-107` |
+| Q-channel enable (boot) | RCSU 0x218 after reset | ✅ Present | `panthor_device.c:196` |
+| Q-channel disable (suspend) | RCSU 0x218 before clk off | ✅ **Implemented** | `panthor_device.c:737-746` |
+| LS_MEM counters | 0x306C/0x3070/0x307C/0x3074 | ✅ Present | `panthor_gpu.c:314-318` |
+| CONFIG_INIT | 0x3068 = 0x1 | ✅ Present | `panthor_gpu.c:318` |
+| PBHA/SYSC_ALLOC | From DTS | ✅ Hardcoded | `panthor_gpu.c:302-310` |
+| PWR_OVERRIDE1 (L2 power) | 0xFFFFFF | ✅ Present | `panthor_gpu.c:321-322` |
+| PWR_OVERRIDE1 (soft reset) | 0xFFFFFF | ✅ Present | `panthor_gpu.c:395-397` |
+| MMU AS_COMMAND workaround | Direct FLUSH_MEM/PT | ✅ Present | `panthor_mmu.c:611-614` |
+| Shader core harvesting | RCSU 0x304 | ⚠️ Uses GPU reg | Functional but different method |
+
+### Register Value Comparison
+
+**PBHA/SYSC_ALLOC Configuration**:
+
+Vendor DTS:
+```dts
+pbha {
+    int_id_override = <0x02 0x23 0x04 0x23 0x10 0x22 0x11 0x32
+                       0x12 0x52 0x15 0x32 0x16 0x52 0x18 0x22 0x1c 0x32>;
+};
+```
+
+Panthor hardcoded (matching vendor values):
+```c
+gpu_write(ptdev, GPU_SYSC_PBHA_OVERRIDE(3), 0x22000000);
+gpu_write(ptdev, GPU_SYSC_ALLOC(0), 0x00230000);
+gpu_write(ptdev, GPU_SYSC_ALLOC(1), 0x00000023);
+gpu_write(ptdev, GPU_SYSC_ALLOC(2), 0x00000000);
+gpu_write(ptdev, GPU_SYSC_ALLOC(3), 0x00000000);
+gpu_write(ptdev, GPU_SYSC_ALLOC(4), 0x00523222);
+gpu_write(ptdev, GPU_SYSC_ALLOC(5), 0x00523200);
+gpu_write(ptdev, GPU_SYSC_ALLOC(6), 0x00000022);
+gpu_write(ptdev, GPU_SYSC_ALLOC(7), 0x00000032);
+```
+
