+
+## Potential Remaining Gaps
+
+### 1. Shader Core Harvesting
+
+Vendor reads RCSU 0x304 to determine which shader cores are available. Panthor uses GPU_SHADER_PRESENT register directly. This should be equivalent but the register value masking differs slightly.
